{"id": 421, "genre": 1001, "title": "说说租房血泪的瞬间吧！", "description": "一个至今没有被互联网思维解决的问题。", "record_count": 2418, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183704DRnfdULASxKm2kbo.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-14T12:00:04Z", "options": [{"id": 3630, "content": "租了开间，快到一年的时候，被房东告知要卖不续租。在同小区租了另一个开间，快到一年的时候，被房东告知要卖不续租。循环中……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 65}, {"id": 3634, "content": "在北京，千万不能通过互联网找房而是实地挑好几个小区再找里面的房子，因为互联网上就算房间照片还看得过去，小区的楼房和楼道可能糟糕得不行：90 年代香港鬼片风格的电梯、房子门外贴了一圈不孕不育及通下水道小广告、晒着邻居内裤的楼道……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317}, {"id": 3638, "content": "没被黑中介坑过根本不好意思说自己北漂过", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141921}, {"id": 3724, "content": "至少比买房便宜吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141037}, {"id": 3770, "content": "被子好脏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142461}, {"id": 3556, "content": "被一起合租的陌生人要求:洗脸用脸盆，洗衣服不要分开洗，洗澡时间要短。嘴上总是说“在外面不容易”，这便是他们苛刻他人的无敌理由。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133375}, {"id": 3557, "content": "想把房东留的所有东西都丢掉而不能", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 3560, "content": "假装 床很干净洗衣机很干净厨房很干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115224}, {"id": 3909, "content": "便宜的房子离市中心太远 市中心的房子又租不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139883}, {"id": 3757, "content": "合租永远男生被歧视，劳资都不得已加一句我是基佬啊?中介要死暴力，每天看房想死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43477}, {"id": 3878, "content": "以上吐糟，好像我住的客派栖家的房子都不符合。我在重庆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143232}, {"id": 3627, "content": "一到周末，楼上的电钻就开始提供叫醒服务。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 73}, {"id": 3620, "content": "被拆", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 20131}, {"id": 3599, "content": "和大学同学租房变成敌人", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3600, "content": "听够了限妹子限女只要女生性别女，难道男生就不要租房子了么！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3601, "content": "说不要中介费或者中介费极少的。都是等着黑你押金，找各种理由，各种耍无赖，各种装黑社会，喷着大碴子味的话黑掉你的押金", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3602, "content": "我就把房东吱吱作响的床给丢到了露台。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 3607, "content": "借着地域优势用不可思议的价格出租，贵就算了，小就算了，最起码你的配备跟上时代吧，哎？不的？就是90年代的格局与色调，纠结，可惜了那个好地段！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141680}, {"id": 3606, "content": "贵！不敢买东西。基本就是凑合着过吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 82077}, {"id": 3604, "content": "月租很难，网上信息八九不离十的都是中介", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141666}, {"id": 3673, "content": "没付房租前说的天花乱坠，付完房租爱答不理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142031}, {"id": 3683, "content": "北京的老房子为什么客厅总是那么小？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126585}, {"id": 4386, "content": "我就想知道中介凭啥收中介费！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146162}, {"id": 3585, "content": "你永远都不会知道那里是个老鼠窝……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77140}, {"id": 6094, "content": "找了一个星期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149663}, {"id": 3584, "content": "不幸遇上二房东简直跟进了鬼屋一样?", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115767}, {"id": 6913, "content": "每天都有东西坏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148312}, {"id": 3586, "content": "中介：和“城乡结合部”、“三不管地带”类似的称呼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141541}, {"id": 3842, "content": "押金就是拿来扣的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142953}, {"id": 3587, "content": "租房完全靠抢啊，每当我还走在郊外的小路上，中介就跟我说不用来了已出", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101671}, {"id": 3589, "content": "房东留下的家私又占地又不实用", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132248}, {"id": 7429, "content": "租了楼顶花园，才发现楼顶夹层成群的老鼠老是在晚上练兵，从此失眠伴我左右", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156188}, {"id": 3590, "content": "信息不对称", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 71634}, {"id": 3592, "content": "工资永远赶不上房租的涨势", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 3593, "content": "中介这个职业真是暴利！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 9787}, {"id": 3596, "content": "当你适应现在的住处时，没准室友或者房东就因为种种原因逼迫你赶紧找新房，在等38℃高温中搬家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 18707, "content": "明明找了一个普装，结果同样的价格给我了一套豪装。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 3869, "content": "到了新城市 花了将近三倍价钱租了一间不通透的回迁房 中介压价就好像他们在收房租一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115708}, {"id": 3618, "content": "您好", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141681}, {"id": 3651, "content": "需要一些力量，来颠覆被中介霸占的租房行业", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141980}, {"id": 179524, "content": "房东儿子要结婚了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723895}, {"id": 152655, "content": "有条件还是一个人住吧，至少幸福感会高一些", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901167}, {"id": 3923, "content": "我有解决办法。", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234802wtFG0idEcbChRZOH.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143336}, {"id": 6753, "content": "在北京我一直用自如友家，不是广告。用过的都知道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152398}, {"id": 3955, "content": "千万不要和关系一般的同学合租，真的会变！敌！人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3465, "content": "一个被中介毁掉的词语——精装修", "image": null, "praise_count": 198, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3466, "content": "豆瓣上合租总是要求是妹子是妹子是妹子，身为男性的我感到悲伤", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3467, "content": "90年代家具品味难看哭，房东又不同意你把家具扔掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3227, "content": "租房网站上全是骗人的图片和骗人的中介，互联网思维完全没用", "image": null, "praise_count": 360, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3231, "content": "拖着巨大型行李箱看房结果房子烂到爆", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}]}